<b><a href="/">ChuckPad</a></b>

enables users to create, curate, and share code from music programming environments.
The project's goal is to promote education, stoke enthusiasm, reduce barriers to entry, and aid in discovery of content in apps like
<a href="http://audicle.cs.princeton.edu/mini/">MiniAudicle</a> and
<a href="https://ccrma.stanford.edu/~spencer/auraglyph/">Auraglyph</a>.<br>
<br>
