  <li>Unit tests to exercise server and iOS SDK - <a href="https://github.com/markcerqueira/hello-chuckpad">hello-chuckpad on GitHub</a></li>
  <li>Docker image for rendering ChucK patches - <a href="https://github.com/markcerqueira/chuck-renderer">chuck-renderer on GitHub</a> /
